ret=CSpeZ18PYG" data-secret="CSpeZ18PYG" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p></p><p></p> <a href="https://p2y.jp/anycolors-ceo-tazumi-riku-released-statement-in-response-to-furious-criticism-of-the-company/">ANYCOLOR 总裁 Riku Takuno 发表声明，回应对该公司的强烈批评。首先</a>出现在<a href="https://p2y.jp">P2y.jp</a>上。; https://p2y.jp/anycolors-ceo-tazumi-riku-released-statement-in-response-to-furious-criticism-of-the-company/feed/ 0 115251
